data.description: Get More for Your Money! Hard to find by 4 Bedroom, 2 Bath. The Home Features a Step-Down Family Room with Gas Fireplace. Granite counters in the kitchen with a wall oven and separate range. Large utility room with plenty of room for storage. The 4th bedroom is used for access to the master bedroom or use it for a home office. Covered Parking, Convenient Location, Covered, rear patio great for Entertaining. Main bathroom has a bathtub and master bathroom has a shower. This is the best priced 4 bedroom in the City of Grants Pass in last 18 months. Don't miss it! All information deemed reliable but not verified and is subject to change without notice. Buyer to do due diligence.
